00:16:08,389 --> 00:16:09,708
Very surprising.

124
00:16:09,817 --> 00:16:13,489
Money is the part which is the blessing of the Lakshmi,

125
00:16:14,037 --> 00:16:15,917
but the Gruha Lakshmi is the one

