00:16:16,033 --> 00:16:19,345
who is a householder, is not respected.

127
00:16:20,556 --> 00:16:23,051
And with this, I tell you,

128
00:16:23,685 --> 00:16:28,049
there’s a… very, very wrong things can happen.

